      "rationale": "Code verification performed by comparing solver output against NAFEMS benchmark LE1 and a closed-form Euler-Bernoulli beam solution for a cantilever loaded in bending. Maximum nodal displacement error < 0.3% for both benchmarks, confirming correct implementation of the linear elastic constitutive model and contact algorithm used in this COU.",
