      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Iterative solver residuals monitored; force residual norm < 1e-6 at every load step. Reaction force equilibrium checked: sum of nodal reaction forces within 0.01% of applied load. No solution divergence or convergence warnings recorded across 11 model instances.",
