      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Model setup reviewed by an independent FEA engineer not involved in the original build. Checklist covering boundary conditions, material assignments, contact definitions, and load application was completed and signed. No use errors identified during independent review. Simulation log files archived for traceability.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
